fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.mapping

Interface ManyReferenceAs<M>

  • Type Parameters:
    M - the type of the references after mapping
    All Superinterfaces:
    ManyReferenceMapper, ManyValueMapper, ReferenceMapper, ValueMapper
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AllReferenceAs<M>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractInMemoryBackend, BoundInMemoryBackend, DefaultInMemoryBackend

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public interface ManyReferenceAs<M>
extends ManyValueMapper, ManyReferenceMapper
    A ManyReferenceMapper that provides a default behavior to use M instead of Id for multi-valued references.
